Sap AG Expands Insurance Offering With Acquisition Of Camilion
Thursday, 7 Mar 2013 10:00am EST
Sap AG announced that it plans to acquire Camilion, a leading provider of insurance product development, product life-cycle and underwriting solutions that help insurance companies significantly improve the quality of the business they write and bring new products to market faster. Camilion was founded in 2001 and is a software company that leading insurers use to gain enterprise-wide agility with their products and underwriting. It is privately held, with offices in Canada and the United States. SAP and Camilion have collaborated since 2008.Â 
